Congratulations to Marissa Vestal for winning our SCCC DECA Ascend scholarship this year! The secret to her success, dedication! “Marketing and DECA have helped me improve my public speaking skills, creativity, and leadership skills. It is important to continue the marketing program as the program not only teaches about marketing but also teaches about how to make a difference.” -Marissa Vestal
#ICDCweek #NextLevel #DECAcompete #SCCCworks
